http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/95/18/10951817_det.jpg", "release_date"=>"2007-09-07"}, {"name"=>"True Grit", "rating"=>96, "user_rating"=>86, "mpaa_rating"=>"PG-13", "description"=>"Fourteen-year-old Mattie Ross (Hailee Steinfeld) joins an aging U.S. marshal (Jeff Bridges) and another lawman (Matt Damon) in tracking her father's killer into hostile Indian territory in Joel and Ethan Coen's adaptation of Charles Portis' original novel. Sticking more closely to the source material than the 1969 feature adaptation starring Western icon John Wayne, the Coens' True Grit tells the story from the young girl's perspective, and re-teams the celebrated filmmaking duo with their No Country for Old Men producing partner Scott Rudin. Josh Brolin and Barry Pepper co-star. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi", "poster"=>"http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/34/11153437_det.jpg", "release_date"=>"2010-12-22"}, {"name"=>"Source Code", "rating"=>91, "user_rating"=>81, "mpaa_rating"=>"PG-13", "description"=>"When decorated soldier Captain Colter Stevens (Jake Gyllenhaal) wakes up in the body of an unknown man, he discovers he's part of a mission to find the bomber of a Chicago commuter train. In an assignment unlike any he's ever known, he learns he's part of a government experiment called the Source Code, a program that enables him to cross over into another man's identity in the last 8 minutes of his life. With a second, much larger target threatening to kill millions in downtown Chicago, Colter re-lives the incident over and over again, gathering clues each time, until he can solve the mystery of who is behind the bombs and prevent the next attack. -- (C) Summit", "poster"=>"http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/64/11156441_det.jpg", "release_date"=>"2011-04-01"}, {"name"=>"Rango", "rating"=>88, "user_rating"=>69, "mpaa_rating"=>"PG", "description"=>"Rango is a sheltered chameleon living as an ordinary family pet, while facing a major identity crisis. After all, how high can you aim when your whole purpose in life is to blend in? When Rango accidentally winds up in the gritty, gun-slinging town of Dirt - a lawless outpost populated by the desert's most wily and whimsical creatures - the less-than-courageous lizard suddenly finds he stands out. Welcomed as the last hope the town has been waiting for, new Sheriff Rango is forced to play his new role to the hilt... -- (C) Paramount", "poster"=>"http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/15/45/11154594_det.jpg", "release_date"=>"2011-03-04"}, {"name"=>"Harry Potter And The Philosopher's Stone", "rating"=>-1, "user_rating"=>89, "mpaa_rating"=>"PG", "description"=>"", "poster"=>"http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/66/11166609_det.jpg", "release_date"=>nil}, {"name"=>"Live Free or Die Hard", "rating"=>81, "user_rating"=>86, "mpaa_rating"=>"PG-13", "description"=>"", "poster"=>"http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/93/34/10933482_det.jpg", "release_date"=>"2007-06-27"}, {"name"=>"The Departed", "rating"=>93, "user_rating"=>92, "mpaa_rating"=>"R", "description"=>"", "poster"=>"http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/67/11166721_det.jpg", "release_date"=>"2006-10-06"}, {"name"=>"X-Men", "rating"=>37, "user_rating"=>72, "mpaa_rating"=>"PG-13", "description"=>"", "poster"=>"http://content8.flixster.com/movie/10/93/36/10933642_det.jpg", "release_date"=>"2009-05-01"}, {"name"=>"Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets", "rating"=>83, "user_rating"=>80, "mpaa_rating"=>"PG", "description"=>"", "poster"=>"http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/15/86/11158606_det.jpg", "release_date"=>"2002-11-15"}, {"name"=>"X2: X-Men United", "rating"=>88, "user_rating"=>84, "mpaa_rating"=>"PG-13", "description"=>"", "poster"=>"http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/13/33/11133378_det.jpg", "release_date"=>"2003-05-02"}, {"name"=>"The Fighter", "rating"=>18, "user_rating"=>27, "mpaa_rating"=>"PG-13", "description"=>"", "poster"=>"http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/12/45/11124512_det.jpg", "release_date"=>"2009-02-27"}, {"n