ries. -- (C) Fox Searchlight", "poster"=>"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/11/15/77/11157747_det.jpg", "release_date"=>"2011-11-18"}, {"name"=>"The Fountain", "rating"=>51, "user_rating"=>73, "mpaa_rating"=>"PG-13", "description"=>"", "poster"=>"http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/70/11167008_det.jpg", "release_date"=>"2006-11-22"}, {"name"=>"50/50", "rating"=>93, "user_rating"=>89, "mpaa_rating"=>"R", "description"=>"Inspired by a true story, 50/50 is an original story about friendship, love, survival and finding humor in unlikely places. Joseph Gordon-Levitt and Seth Rogen star as best friends whose lives are changed by a cancer diagnosis in this new comedy directed by Jonathan Levine from a script by Will Reiser. 50/50 is the story of a guy's transformative and, yes, sometimes funny journey to health - drawing its emotional core from Will Reiser's own experience with cancer and reminding us that friendship and love, no matter what bizarre turns they take, are the greatest healers. -- (C) Summit Entertainment", "poster"=>"http://content8.flixster.com/movie/11/15/86/11158694_det.jpg", "release_date"=>"2011-09-30"}, {"name"=>"Zodiac", "rating"=>90, "user_rating"=>73, "mpaa_rating"=>"R", "description"=>"", "poster"=>"http://content7.flixster.com/movie/34/10/49/3410497_det.jpg", "release_date"=>"2007-03-02"}, {"name"=>"Kiss Kiss Bang Bang", "rating"=>83, "user_rating"=>83, "mpaa_rating"=>"R", "description"=>"", "poster"=>"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/88/59/10885939_det.jpg", "release_date"=>"2005-10-21"}, {"name"=>"Anchorman: The Legend of Ron Burgundy", "rating"=>66, "user_rating"=>84, "mpaa_rating"=>"PG-13", "description"=>"", "poster"=>"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/88/85/10888587_det.jpg", "release_date"=>"2004-07-09"}, {"name"=>"Mad Max 2: The Road Warrior", "rating"=>100, "user_rating"=>76, "mpaa_rating"=>"R", "description"=>"", "poster"=>"http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/86/48/10864824_det.jpg", "release_date"=>"1981-12-24"}, {"name