itants of the planet, including Tars Tarkas (Willem Dafoe) and the captivating Princess Dejah Thoris (Lynn Collins). In a world on the brink of collapse, Carter rediscovers his humanity when he realizes that the survival of Barsoom and its people rests in his hands. -- (C) Walt Disney", "poster"=>"http://content6.flixster.com/movie/11/16/39/11163924_det.jpg", "release_date"=>"2012-03-09"}, {"name"=>"Resident Evil", "rating"=>22, "user_rating"=>63, "mpaa_rating"=>"R", "description"=>"", "poster"=>"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/93/47/10934787_det.jpg", "release_date"=>"2007-09-21"}, {"name"=>"Safe House", "rating"=>53, "user_rating"=>65, "mpaa_rating"=>"R", "description"=>"Denzel Washington and Ryan Reynolds star in the action-thriller Safe House. Washington plays the most dangerous renegade from the CIA, who comes back onto the grid after a decade on the run. When the South African safe house he's remanded to is attacked by mercenaries, a rookie operative (Reynolds) escapes with him. Now, the unlikely allies must stay alive long enough to uncover who wants them dead. -- (C) Official Site", "poster"=>"http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/16/54/11165485_det.jpg", "release_date"=>"2012-02-10"}, {"name"=>"The Incredible Hulk", "rating"=>67, "user_rating"=>75, "mpaa_rating"=>"PG-13", "description"=>"", "poster"=>"http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/84/92/10849216_det.jpg", "release_date"=>"2008-06-12"}, {"name"=>"Wanted", "rating"=>71, "user_rating"=>72, "mpaa_rating"=>"R", "description"=>"", "poster"=>"http://content7.flixster.com/movie/10/88/26/10882637_det.jpg", "release_date"=>"2008-06-12"}, {"name"=>"28 Weeks Later", "rating"=>71, "user_rating"=>66, "mpaa_rating"=>"R", "description"=>"", "poster"=>"http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/86/37/10863760_det.jpg", "release_date"=>"2007-05-11"}, {"name"=>"1408", "rating"=>78, "user_rating"=>61, "mpaa_rating"=>"PG-13", "description"=>"", "poster"=>"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/85/59/06/8559063_det.jpg", "r