/16/41/11164141_det.jpg", "release_date"=>"2012-01-20"}, {"name"=>"Night at the Museum 2: Battle of the Smithsonian", "rating"=>43, "user_rating"=>60, "mpaa_rating"=>"PG", "description"=>"", "poster"=>"http://content6.flixster.com/movie/10/93/20/10932000_det.jpg", "release_date"=>"2009-05-22"}, {"name"=>"Fright Night", "rating"=>73, "user_rating"=>60, "mpaa_rating"=>"R", "description"=>"Senior Charlie Brewster (Anton Yelchin) finally has it all-he's running with the popular crowd and dating the hottest girl in high school. In fact, he's so cool he's even dissing his best friend Ed (Christopher Mintz-Plasse). But trouble arrives when an intriguing stranger Jerry (Colin Farrell) moves in next door. He seems like a great guy at first, but there's something not quite right-and everyone, including Charlie's mom (Toni Collette), doesn't notice. After witnessing some very unusual activity, Charlie comes to an unmistakable conclusion: Jerry is a vampire preying on his neighborhood. Unable to convince anyone that he's telling the truth, Charlie has to find a way to get rid of the monster himself in this revamp of the comedy-horror classic. -- (C) DreamWorks", "poster"=>"http://content7.flixster.com/movie/11/15/75/11157537_det.jpg", "release_date"=>"2011-08-19"}, {"name"=>"Over the Top", "rating"=>36, "user_rating"=>51, "mpaa_rating"=>"PG", "description"=>"", "poster"=>"http://content8.flixster.com/movie/57/07/95/5707950_det.jpg", "release_date"=>"1987-02-13"}, {"name"=>"Harold & Kumar: Escape from Guantanamo Bay", "rating"=>54, "user_rating"=>65, "mpaa_rating"=>"R", "description"=>"", "poster"=>"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/10/82/71/10827119_det.jpg", "release_date"=>"2008-04-24"}, {"name"=>"Spy Game", "rating"=>65, "user_rating"=>70, "mpaa_rating"=>"R", "description"=>"", "poster"=>"http://content9.flixster.com/movie/74/09/11/7409119_det.jpg", "release_date"=>"2001-11-21"}, {"name"=>"Chaos", "rating"=>20, "user_rating"=>62, "mpaa_rating"=>"R", "description"=>"", "post